</taxonomicName>
by the very finely punctate lateral parts of the metaventrite.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B995A6CFFE5FFBC67206D67FBA3BDF3" blockId="14.[831,1437,1115,1170]" pageId="14" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis id="B952867EFFE5FFBC67206D67FC12BD13" bold="true" box="[831,928,1115,1138]" pageId="14" pageNumber="117">Habitat:</emphasis>
